### Service Desk API — quick tests
### Requires the VS Code extension "REST Client" (id: humao.rest-client).
### Click "Send Request" above each block.

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### 1. Health
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### 2. Register a new user (gets a token + REQUESTER role)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Gabrielly",
  "email": "gabi@test.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 3. Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "gabi@test.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 4. Me — paste the token from step 2 or 3 after "Bearer "
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
